# no trailing slash: `node_modules/` matches only a DIRECTORY, so a node_modules
# SYMLINK (e.g. linked into a throwaway worktree) slips past `git add -A` and, once
# committed, materializes on the live checkout as a self-pointing ELOOP that fails
# the supervisor's build gate (quarantined d9b87d3d, 2026-07-05).
node_modules
dist/
*.log
.env
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-*
.wt/
# local runtime: per-operator config + the daemon's local clone of the target
.ralph/config.yaml
.ralph/daemon.pid
.ralph/tmp/
# self-update coordination record (supervisor writes, daemon reads/clears, #30)
.ralph/quarantine
.target-repo/
# local Serena MCP tooling scaffolding (auto-generated per-operator; not repo state)
.serena/
